    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>State, condition, or behavior in which a person's identity does not conform unambiguously to conventional notions of male or female gender, including transsexualism or transvestism.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
